3
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:17,719
There are some, indeed.

4
00:00:18,719 --> 00:00:19,440
But...

5
00:00:20,559 --> 00:00:22,160
Look who the trader is.

6
00:00:25,523 --> 00:00:27,936
(Buyer Qin Muyi bought it
from merchant Cuba.)

7
00:00:28,239 --> 00:00:29,320
Qin Muyi?

8
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:32,119
She cares so much about you.

9
00:00:32,399 --> 00:00:33,840
No reason she'd harm your mother.

10
00:00:36,520 --> 00:00:37,439
This morning,

11
00:00:38,840 --> 00:00:40,439
she sent over some pastries.

12
00:00:47,399 --> 00:00:48,200
What?

13
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:53,840
Today is the memorial day
of Concubine Yu.

14
00:00:58,759 --> 00:00:59,759
Not tell you

15
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,719
just not to make you feel confined.

16
00:01:01,840 --> 00:01:02,640
Here.

17
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,719
Your Highness.

18
00:01:24,680 --> 00:01:26,560
The offerings for Concubine Yu
are ready.

19
