(Chunhui Garden)

20
00:01:35,763 --> 00:01:37,440
♪The wind picks up at night♪

21
00:01:38,048 --> 00:01:40,832
♪Stirring feelings just that profound♪

22
00:01:41,824 --> 00:01:45,472
♪Never expect a parting to last forever♪

23
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:49,319
Yue?

24
00:01:50,016 --> 00:01:53,216
♪Feel the poetry in wilted blooms♪

25
00:01:53,760 --> 00:01:57,760
♪Paintings are done, but no destination♪

26
00:01:59,763 --> 00:02:01,952
♪Memories resurface♪

27
